Role lifted her helmet to rub her eyes. She looked at Searchman, but only hesitated a second. Her arms wrapped around him in a tight, tight hug. She didn&#39;t linger, for his comfort. 

She placed her hands to the glass, and brushed away where her breath fogged it. Pen could see his eyes. Life. She blinked away from the glass and stared at Izabella.

&quot;He, uhh- he wants to come here. Now. I can&#39;t be away from him for long. He might hurt himself.&quot; She finally looked at Searchman, for he was the one really talking now. It was a small change, but a welcome one.</span>

