Her arms opened, quietly offering her an embrace. 

&quot;I should go back to him. He&#39;s waiting. I&#39;ll... I&#39;ll try to get him to sleep a little. He&#39;s tired enough for it.&quot; She smiled, apologetic and teary.</span>

