                        <div class="markdown">
                            <span class="preserve-whitespace">Finally, too much time had passed. Enzan jolted awake from the very beginnings of sleep. Pen followed suit, gripping her chest when the surprise was too much. 

&quot;Penelope,&quot; Enzan snapped. His hand came out to grip her arm. She blinked, trying to find calm in the familiar face, but finding none. Her dreams had been just as filled with anxiety as this was. 

&quot;Pen! Get me the wheelchair. Now!&quot; Enzan&#39;s voice was only low enough not to carry outside the room. 

&quot;O-okay. I&#39;m sorry,&quot; Pen hushed. She stood up quickly and pulled her arm free from his grip. Enzan&#39;s eyebrows creased when she reached up and held the spot. Too much. 

Out in the hallway, Pen held her PET in her lap and sunk to the floor next to the wheelchair. Updates. The ventilator came off without trouble. He wasn&#39;t responding to much. He was still awake... Izabella had to leave for the night. Pen sighed and rested her forehead on the cool plastic. After two slow breaths, she wobbled to her feet and pushed the chair into Enzan&#39;s room. 

Enzan had tossed his blankets to the floor and hoisted his legs over the side of the bed. Pen honestly didn&#39;t know how he was sitting up like that with all the bandages still around his head and chest. 

&quot;Help me down.&quot; He ordered. Pen nodded and very gently worked her arm under his thighs. She lifted him, and he leaned into her shoulder to avoid shouting his pain. And down into the chair he went. 

&quot;They might keep me from seeing you after this,&quot; Pen warned. 

&quot;Let&#39;s just go. Please,&quot; Enzan said. He looked at her without the snarl. His deep blue eyes reflected the only light in the room. Her feet started tapping along the linoleum, and soon they were at the elevator. ICU.</span>

                        </div>
                    </div>



            </div>
            <div class="chatlog__message " data-message-id="734747035286241421" id="message-734747035286241421" title="Message sent: 20-Jul-20 08:22 AM">
